# Per-scenario baked grids — large binary blobs, deterministically
# reproducible from the source grib2 via `bywind-cli search --save-baked`.
# Don't commit them; the configs in this directory tell anyone how to
# regenerate them.
*.bk1
*.bake
*.baked

# Per-scenario search-result JSONs. Reproducible from the configs +
# baked grids; keeping them out of git avoids noise.
*.json

# PSO-tuning study artifacts: trial journal (`tune` subcommand's
# JournalStorage output) and scratch baseline JSON. Reproducible by
# re-running `bywind-cli tune` / `tune-trial` against the same configs.
*.jsonl

# Stderr capture from `bywind-cli tune` runs. Same logical status as
# the `.jsonl` journal — reproducible study artifact, not source.
*.log
